{"tid":1018551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[悲哀] 貓義工偷貓事件已經有個規律","createTime":"2019-02-12T10:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T09:41:13.000Z","uid":15696,"like":83,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb6f8d1aa07a92dd4b9f667290157b723d7b9b3","tid":1018551,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">貓義工偷貓 &gt; 原主人發現 &gt; 貓義工唔認 &gt; 偷偷將佢送畀某個「好心人」 &gt; 貓義工話隻貓唔係佢到 &gt; 「好心人」話對隻貓有感情 &gt; 唔肯送返隻貓 &gt; 主人只能同隻貓分離</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFacebook都見唔少，淨係連登近排已經有兩單：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Case1: 真係好想攞返隻貓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/975211\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/975211</a><br />\n</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJ9WL24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJ9WL24.png&h=37284418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SnQQuP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SnQQuP.png&h=0ee0cda3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Case2: 貓義工偷貓，跪求連登仔幫幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1004763\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1004763</a><br />\n</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4jPmBy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4jPmBy.png&h=0a022516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母，啲貓義工真係已經痴撚咗線，執咗人哋隻貓，剪撚咗人哋條貓帶就話人地係流浪貓，踢爆之後一定會話之前嗰主人對隻貓點唔好，總之隻貓係自己到就最好，明明自己屋企細養成十幾隻貓，咁迫對隻貓好？笑撚死人咩，只係想自己個心有滿足感，再唔係可以post文拎光環！仲可以拎返收養人一百幾十。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好心人更加係on撚柒鳩，對隻貓有感情所以唔肯畀返隻貓人？首先，隻貓係人哋嘅財產。第二，你哋對隻貓對得幾日，咁就好有感情？有冇諗過人哋對隻貓對咗幾個月，甚至幾年呀？你根本就係縮骨貪人哋隻貓，你呢啲心態又可以點對隻貓好？有心領養SPCA大把上咗年紀嘅非名種貓你又唔領養？食屎啦！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主人亦都係！養得貓就唔該你小心啲啦！開門倒垃圾就鎖返佢入籠/房，佢走咗出去，真係得25%搵得返，唔好計貓義工，次次執貓post有幾多連登仔話要領養/走去執，就知香港人幾貪小便宜，走咗你貼幾多街招重酬都冇用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[size=5]祝偷貓貓義工同拎咗人貓唔還嘅撚樣百病纏身，死後不得全屍！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [size=5]"},{"pid":"ea4c2201ef4f9082c6ec30ab24db2a462c409d79","tid":1018551,"uid":15696,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">祝偷貓貓義工同拎咗人貓唔還嘅撚樣百病纏身，死後不得全屍！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"c50e6b667098f2c7b735938565c536b74bd11389","tid":1018551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"偷貓賊"},{"pid":"adaa80477b8edd0014ebf62220b80d128ac7c05b","tid":1018551,"uid":11148,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:28:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請購買代替領養，有冇諗過領養既貓全部貓義工（偷貓賊）偷人地既貓黎發財</span></span>"},{"pid":"8f93686a50047af24ed5b228e72a1bbf95d5cc83","tid":1018551,"uid":15696,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己睇實啲隻貓，唔好渴望放上網有人幫你，啲人已經對貓義工偷貓麻木咗，嗰兩個post連1001都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"99705142c5d1de03fe96de1a448c504177e25f3b","tid":1018551,"uid":35014,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:28:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c826463fc463e4473b1a090f8ef6dc2e2bef87da","tid":1018551,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"點解可以日日都有人唔見貓狗？"},{"pid":"f2930aee9d444836336f1e0bee205951a9e63a57","tid":1018551,"uid":15696,"like":0,"d